SELECT 'B0229' AS FACTORID,

        COUNT(DISTINCT TAB1.FIRSTCHECKID) AS FACTORVALUE,

        C.JGBM AS ICPCODE,

        TO_DATE('V_END', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS ATOMDATE,

        TO_DATE('V_CURRENT', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS HANDLETIME,

        C.JGBM AS SEND_NODE,

        TO_DATE('V_CURRENT', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS SEND_TIME

FROM

(

SELECT FIRSTCHECKID,ARCHIVEID FROM ORACLE_GAINUSERNAME.EHEALTH_LADY_FIRSTCHECK WHERE TRIM(PREGNANT_WEEKS)<14 AND REGEXP_LIKE(PREGNANT_WEEKS,'(^[+-]?d{0,}.?d{0,}$)')  AND BOOKING_DATE BETWEEN TO_DATE('V_START', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND TO_DATE('V_END 23:59:59', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') UNION ALL

SELECT FIRSTCHECKID,ARCHIVEID FROM ORACLE_GAINUSERNAME.EHEALTH_LADY_FETIFEROUSCHECK WHERE TRIM(PREGNANCYWEEK)<14 AND REGEXP_LIKE(PREGNANCYWEEK,'(^[+-]?d{0,}.?d{0,}$)')  AND CHECKDATE BETWEEN TO_DATE('V_START', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND TO_DATE('V_END 23:59:59', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') )TAB1

INNER JOIN

(

SELECT FIRSTCHECKID FROM(

SELECT FIRSTCHECKID FROM ORACLE_GAINUSERNAME.EHEALTH_LADY_FIRSTCHECK

UNION ALL

SELECT FIRSTCHECKID FROM ORACLE_GAINUSERNAME.EHEALTH_LADY_FETIFEROUSCHECK

) GROUP BY FIRSTCHECKID HAVING COUNT(*)>4

) TAB2 ON TAB1.FIRSTCHECKID=TAB2.FIRSTCHECKID

INNER JOIN

(

SELECT FIRSTCHECKID FROM(

SELECT FIRSTCHECKID FROM ORACLE_GAINUSERNAME.EHEALTH_LADY_VISIT42DAYS WHERE VISIT_DATE BETWEEN TO_DATE('V_START', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND TO_DATE('V_END 23:59:59', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')

UNION ALL

SELECT FIRSTCHECKID FROM ORACLE_GAINUSERNAME.EHEALTH_LADY_VISITS WHERE CHECKDATE BETWEEN TO_DATE('V_START', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND TO_DATE('V_END 23:59:59', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')

) GROUP BY FIRSTCHECKID HAVING COUNT(*)>1

)TAB3 ON TAB2.FIRSTCHECKID=TAB3.FIRSTCHECKID  INNER JOIN ORACLE_GAINUSERNAME.EHEALTH_ARCH_BASICINFO EAB ON TAB1.ARCHIVEID=EAB.ARCHID

INNER JOIN ORACLE_GAINUSERNAME.T_GOVINFO_POPULATION C ON EAB.RESIDENTCOMMITTEE=C.GOVCODE

INNER JOIN ORACLE_GAINUSERNAME.T_GOVINFO TG  ON C.JGBM=TG.JGBM
